INSERT INTO `articles_mask` (`post`,`native_id`,`post_account_id`,`post_type`) VALUES ("After playing part of the exchange between the two, Cuomo stated that Fauci canâ€™t make the rules about protest restrictions. He continued, â€œWhy not ask the president why he celebrated the maskless gun guys in Michigan, or at his rallies, or his mask mocking, that even you play along with, congressman.â€\n After playing another clip, where Jordan asked about the constitutionality of treating protests and religious gatherings differently, and Fauci stating that heâ€™s making a general statement that crowds should be avoided, Cuomo said, â€œFauciâ€™s a practicing Catholic, what does Jordan want to say? Fauci hates Christians. Social distancing is a hoax to crush Jesus. Fauci didnâ€™t make the rules. Talk to gym owners if you want to talk about being unfairly excluded. This isnâ€™t about keeping people from praying, itâ€™s about praying that people act more like Jesus commanded, being your brotherâ€™s keeper.â€\n Cuomo later stated, â€œWhy didnâ€™t you ask him, how do we do better? How can you guys help us with the testing? How can you help us get results faster so that people arenâ€™t making their whole family sick while theyâ€™re waiting for the result for a test? 3,500 people in Ohio have died, 11,000 are hospitalized or were, and youâ€™re worried about the protests.â€","1674497418","3","2");
